Class BTOApplicationWithdrawal

Object
BTOApplicationWithdrawal
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class BTOApplicationWithdrawal extends Object implements Serializable
Represents an applicant's request to withdraw from a BTO Application. See BTOApplicationWithdrawalStatus for possible statuses.
